      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "### Federation (n=5) \u2014 the live watch board\nThe operator single-pane for the live cloud: **overall** + **gossip** (rejection rate = the storm early-warning) + **finality** (per-node height, finality age, attested/quorum, vote-share) + the **rust\u2194lean differential** + **conservation** + the **lapse driver** + **settlement meter**.\n\nGossip rejection rate and the differential are the two RED-on-incident panels. Native `dregg_*` come straight off each node's `/metrics`; `dreggnet_ops_*` come via the ops `/api/health` json-exporter. Per-node breakouts key off the `instance` label, so the board fills out as nodes are added to the scrape set. Runbook: `runbooks/INCIDENT-RESPONSE.md`."
